{"tid":144102,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"1000不直 ac68u無死？","createTime":"2017-03-05T07:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T11:23:13.000Z","uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c624b18dbb6dbb8db75e71bf2229558b10fd0b2","tid":144102,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:02:24.000Z","msg":"追左少少舊post<br />\n來來去去都r7000 r7800 ac68u ac58u 同唔好買tplink咁<br />\n原先主要係for macbook 手機 上網<br />\n依家用緊pcc 500mbs 完約去我1gbs<br />\n諗落直接買貴少少用多幾年好過<br />\n預用3年至4年<br />\n我諗家用未咁快上多過1gbs掛(generally)<br />\n<br />\n除ac68u 仲有冇其他推介？<br />\n佢寫可以上到1900 ，但實質1gbs可以上到幾多？<br />\ngearnet好似唔建議用，咩有害之類<br />\n求指教"},{"pid":"1fb7d4bfe3ebe4a169a0852862fd58ec59126941","tid":144102,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:57:39.000Z","msg":"router budget 1000或以下幾乎永遠都係ASUS RT-AC68U vs Netgear R7000 大戰<br />\n呢兩隻我建議你鍾意邊隻買邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97611ea68aabed7d0fc2db53d1a8911068efc47","tid":144102,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:31:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>router budget 1000或以下幾乎永遠都係ASUS RT-AC68U vs Netgear R7000 大戰<br />\n呢兩隻我建議你鍾意邊隻買邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都仲係唔知頭唔知路咁<br />\n無話鍾意邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但ac68u好似話有D煩？有時又斷下線咁<br />\n<br />\nbtw係咪我講錯咩<br />\n可唔可以比下意見唔好只係落負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbef873eea8184ae35ee94e2b9e2982f5363423","tid":144102,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:41:09.000Z","msg":"Ac68u個hs cut料<br />\n同埋usb3.0慢過同級"},{"pid":"664643f333161e5dee0ea24d16f4ff88a95942cd","tid":144102,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ac68u個hs cut料<br />\n同埋usb3.0慢過同級</blockquote><br />\n咁有冇其他推介<img src=\"/as